{"tid":1814782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"退場宣言 各位手足保重","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T05:22:48.000Z","uid":137406,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45203f1eaafa52761b4c9041e198c316015ec5cd","tid":1814782,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"大家好，我地係一隊原本約有20人嘅反利小隊。無名嘅，不過見原來大家都咁鐘意改名，我地為咗出呢篇文就改翻個，叫「油尖旺仇利聯」。點解我話原本20人，因為我地有2個前線成員加埋其中一位手足「愛迪克愛助攻」由2年前已經失聯，我地姑且當佢走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢幾日都見好多小隊因爲各種原因話要退出戰線：捉鬼，怕死，驚累屋企等等⋯⋯所以我地隊經慎重考慮正式退場。但願有緣能煲底相見，利物浦降班之時就是反利重光之日。"},{"pid":"abb69b1dcf1ce41302768bef2ea36da4cfb4c888","tid":1814782,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"愛迪生愛助攻"},{"pid":"62bac6b66b0b2c1e4cb8252f70b2e1482c6e8751","tid":1814782,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"abb69b1dcf1ce41302768bef2ea36da4cfb4c888","tid":1814782,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"愛迪生愛助攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a02e498356748364e0e7ed6afa72c8f26f5b72","tid":1814782,"uid":305137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">75m買個契弟小醜</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}